article.description: — Justin Bean recorded 13 points and 13 rebounds as Utah State extended its winning streak to eight games, routing New Mexico 82-46 on Friday night.
article.headline: Bean carries Utah St. over New Mexico 82-46
article.linkText: Bean carries Utah St. over New Mexico 82-46
article.story: LUBBOCK, Texas -- — Justin Bean recorded 13 points and 13 rebounds as Utah State extended its winning streak to eight games, routing New Mexico 82-46 on Friday night. Neemias Queta added 11 points and 13 rebounds for the Aggies. Queta also had three blocks. Marco Anthony had 12 points and eight rebounds for Utah State (9-3, 6-0 Mountain West Conference). Steven Ashworth added 10 points. Makuach Maluach had 13 points for the Lobos (3-6, 0-6), whose losing streak stretched to six games. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
